-- Liberty Mutual’s Long Seeks Acquisitions to Expand Outside U.S.
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-01-10T21:03:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-10/liberty-mutual-s-long-seeks-acquisitions-to-expand-outside-u-s-.html
Liberty Mutual Holding Co., the
largest policyholder-owned workers’ compensation insurer in the
U.S., may expand through acquisitions in other nations, Chief
Executive Officer David Long said.  The insurer will be active in the mergers-and-acquisitions
market and expects growth in premium revenue from emerging
economies, Long said at an industry conference today in  New
York . Liberty Mutual is based in  Boston .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  